D. Acquisition Strategy
Air Force Research Laboratory (AFRL) will conduct research/studies to develop/implement Cross Domain Solutions (CDS) supporting integrated DMO and Live-
synthetic blended training. Fielded and projected Air Force flight and mission training systems without blended training capability and will be modified to ensure training
compatibility.




