facilities, avionics test facilities, aircraft testbeds, dry lakebed landing sites, instrumented test ranges, and test aircraft maintenance, as well as USAF Test Pilot School.

 The AFTC's three Test Wings (TW) are supported by this project:(1) Arnold Engineering and Development Complex (AEDC), located at Arnold Air Force Base (AFB) TN;
