Title: Strike Assets                                                                                                                               -              0.000     211.370
Description: Strike Assets are the offensive components that operate within the "web" of the Long-Range Kill Web (LRKW)
concept. Their primary purpose is to create a cohesive and lethal strike capability that can penetrate deep into contested airspace,
engage targets with precision, return to base, and repeat the mission.

