food safety and develop improved systems for waste management and resource utilization in operational settings. Finally, the
program will invest in next-generation water security, focusing on innovative water sourcing and purification technologies to
counter emerging threats, ensuring the foundational elements of Warfighter readiness are secure and technologically superior.

