construct, identification, location, and associated activities. The TVS/RSTA provides Global Combatant
Commanders and SOF operators with an immediate capability to visually and electronically identify people,
things, and activities and provides actionable intelligence for SOF planners and Commanders. The Family
of Systems consists of interoperable equipment to capture and transfer near-real-time ground-based, tactical
day/night/reduced visibility, imagery, video, and electronic proximity and movement sensing, all capable of


