       The FY 2026 request for Operational Enhancements includes $234.653 million of discretionary and $34.750 million of mandatory (reconciliation) for a total
       of $269.403 million. Further information for this reconciliation request is provided in Section 20010 (Readiness) of the Reconciliation Exhibit. The following
       justifications reflect the sum totals of mandatory (reconciliation) and discretionary categories of funding.




