Projection (SP), Unmanned Ground Vehicle (UGV), and Unmanned Aerial Vehicle (UAV). Previously reported
variant NGLS- Mounted (M) variant transferred to US Army.

FY 2025 Plans:
NGLS-D: continue development in FY25 into FY26. Test and evaluation will begin in 4th QTR 2026.
FY 2026 Base Plans:
NGLS-D: continue development in FY 2025 into FY 2026. Test and evaluation will begin in 4th quarter FY 2026.
