- Develop systematic methods to discover new numerical algorithms; assess efficacy by rediscovering known numerical
algorithms and algorithm structures.
- Extend algorithm discovery methods to search for new algorithms and algorithm structures.
- Demonstrate optimization methods to systematically discover new algorithms and new algorithm structures, especially new
hybrid classical-machine learning algorithm combinations.
- Develop mathematical methods to systematically find transformations that simplify DoD relevant modeling problems.
